values:
Today: Today was boring I did not want to wake up in the morning. School was pretty much the same boring. After school i went out and finished getting all most of my stuff for some classes. This is where im at now filling this thing out early.

Yesterday:woke up for the first day of school. Most of my teachers were cool till they gave us the same shit to fill out in every class.came home after school i didn't do much i just went on the computer all day. boring day i guess.

today was cool. Went and visited one of my old teachers i mean like 1st grade old, but it was cool. After that went to my dad's work to get my last check. I had it on friday but the my boss forgot to sign the bottom of it so i couldn't cash it. went back today he was there so got it signed and went an cashed it. Spent most of the day with my mom only cus she wouldnt let me stay home Damn parents. After all of that we went shopping for some school stuff, pens and notebooks stuff like that.
After that i came home went on the computer for a lil and my dad came home so we went to my cousins new house. This house is cool,i should say the backyard is cool.
Theres this little club house i guess u can call it that w/e its sweet. It has cable, power, and phone line in it u could live in there. theres also a little chipping green in the back for golf. good thing i didnt have any money to bet cause i would of lost it against my cousin. stayed there for a couple of hours then went home and thats where im at now. see everybody tomorrow 

Adam

just another post,figured some more stuff out yeah i think i am going to bed it 2:25 i think.  
Good night 

Adam
